  "title": "Service Technician / Service Engineer #78639",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Marine/ Oil & Gas</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Service Technician / Service Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Loyang (Transport provided)</li><li>Working Hours: Monday to Friday, 9am – 6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + OT + Variable Bonus (Twice yearly)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform production, servicing, installation, and commissioning of equipment.</li><li>Communicate additional customer requirements to your supervisor.</li><li>Receive and inspect customer-supplied products.</li><li>Ensure all jobs meet technical manual standards and customer requirements.</li><li>Provide cabling diagrams for customers as needed.</li><li>Commission equipment after installation.</li><li>Identify and report quality issues to the Service Manager.</li><li>Supervise technicians during production, servicing, installation, and commissioning.</li><li>Approve release of equipment to customers after successful service and installation.</li><li>Decide on the placement/location for new installation work.</li><li>Supervise sub-contractors on the job site.</li><li>Prepare and approve service reports.</li><li>Carry out additional tasks as assigned by the section manager or supervisor.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum NTC/ITC in Electronics Engineering or equivalent, with at least five (5) years of relevant experience.</li><li>Sound knowledge of computers, electronics, and telecommunication systems.</li><li>Experience in marine electronics or the offshore industry is an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78639 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
